<% af_category "Exterior Signage" do %>
  <p>
    Do not be afraid to spend money on a nice sign! Having a large, well-lit professional sign is one of the
    best way to attract customers. Additionally, if your store is located in a shopping center or mall,
    be aware of their rules for signage. You may not want to have a location where local management restricts
    the kinds of signs you can have. Be sure to negotiate signs before you sign any kind of lease, some locations will not
    allow you to change your signage agreement after signing.
  </p>
